org.dyn4j.dynamics

Class Island

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dyn4j.dynamics.Island

  • public class Island
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to solve the contact constraints and joints for a group of interconnected bodies.

    Nearly identitcal to Box2d's equivalent class.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    3.1.5
    Author:
    William Bittle
    See Also:
    Box2d
